<li class="ui-state-default ui-corner-top" style="list-style: none; border-top: 1px solid #c5dbec; border-right: 1px solid #c5dbec; border-bottom: 0px !important; border-left: 1px solid #c5dbec; border-image: initial; background: url('images/ui-bg_glass_85_dfeffc_1x400.png') 50% 50% repeat-x #dfeffc; font-weight: bold; color: #2e6e9e; border-top-left-radius: 5px; border-top-right-radius: 5px; font-size: 14px; line-height: 24px; text-indent: 0px; opacity: 1 !important; float: left; position: relative; top: 1px; margin: 0px 0.2em 1px 0px; padding: 0px; white-space: nowrap;"><a href="http://www.rpcformacion.es/cursosonline/pluginfile.php/5432/mod_scorm/content/1/cargador.html?r=VVQ5dUxuJTJGbkZCUnNzMVZNOVVmbHd3MnNUSjhLM2JEMmdlUW1LTEtROTFralh0OG5SVjdPbWNMYU5ucGJVdWNycCUyRndKVzdGR3Y0VXNZZnRucmtxWjVnJTNEJTNE&amp;p=TDBTWGJDdDFZUHVHNVN0QSUyQlNhVnR4RDFUTUh1VEZ1WXNUd2FINWJIaXJzJTNE&amp;v=HTM_MjBJY1h5RjZOVjJuZFhTdTBydlZpaHhmSmVScW1jVEJHQVNlOG5iZ1h1VSUzRA==&amp;c=SUxVamxkbzUlMkJuUmpocUVGWTdLR0VaR3JjcDVjR3BuUkZuJTJCJTJCYktXeWdKUSUzRA==&amp;t=3.3.%20Digesti%C3%B3n%20de%20los%20l%C3%ADpidos#tabs-3" style="color: #4b8fc7; text-decoration: none; font-size: 12px; float: left; padding: 0.5em 1em; cursor: pointer; vertical-align: middle;">Fosfolipasa</a></li>
</ul>
<div id="tabs-1" class="ui-tabs-panel ui-widget-content ui-corner-bottom" style="border: 0px solid #a6c9e2; background: none; color: #222222; border-bottom-left-radius: 5px; border-bottom-right-radius: 5px; display: block; padding: 1em 1.4em; outline: none;">Es muy fuerte. Transforma los triglicéridos en monoglicéridos y ácidos grasos.</div>
</div>
